   191→                
   192→                <p>In this comprehensive Premier League 2025/26 preview, we'll dive into detailed team-by-team analysis, including tactical breakdowns, key player profiles with 2024/25 stats, major transfers, strengths, weaknesses, and expert-backed Premier League predictions. Drawing from sources like ESPN, BBC, Opta, and CBS Sports, where Liverpool holds a 73.4% top-four probability, we've crafted bold forecasts for the full table. Whether you're betting on the Golden Boot race or scouting promoted teams like Sunderland, Leeds United, and Burnley, this guide covers it all for optimal Premier League fantasy tips and insights.</p>
